    },
    "content": [
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "If your sales team lives on the phone, sends dozens of texts daily, and runs multi-step email sequences, you already know most CRMs weren't built for you. Close was. And in 2025, it just got a serious upgrade.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "I've been tracking Close for a while now, and the recent updates genuinely changed how I think about what a sales CRM can do. We're not talking about cosmetic changes. We're talking about an AI agent that picks up the phone and books meetings while you sleep.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [
          {
            "_key": "l0",
            "_type": "link",
            "href": "https://refer.close.com/bf9dumgltl5q"
          }
        ],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "See Close's full feature set and start your free trial",
            "marks": [
              "l0"
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Let me walk you through everything that's new, why it matters, and who's going to benefit most from these changes.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "---",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h2",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "What is Close and Why Does It Matter in 2025?",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [
          {
            "_key": "l1",
            "_type": "link",
            "href": "https://tonyciencia.com/en/posts/what-is-close"
          }
        ],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "If you're new here, ",
            "marks": []
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Close is a sales CRM",
            "marks": [
              "l1"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " built specifically for inside sales teams. It's not a generic platform stretched thin across marketing, support, and sales. Close focuses on one thing: helping salespeople close deals faster.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "The platform combines calling, email, SMS, pipeline management, and reporting into a single interface. No tab-switching. No duct-taped integrations between your phone system and your CRM. Everything happens in one place.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "With over 11,500 businesses trusting Close and more than 2 billion calls, emails, and texts processed, the platform has serious scale behind it. A 4.7-star rating on G2 from 2,000+ reviews tells you users aren't just satisfied—they're vocal about it.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "But the real story in 2025 isn't just what Close has always done well. It's what it can now do automatically.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "---",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h2",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Meet Chloe: The AI Sales Agent Built Into Your CRM",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Here's where things get exciting.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Close introduced ",
            "marks": []
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Chloe",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": ", an AI sales agent that's native to the platform. Not an integration. Not a third-party tool you bolt on and hope plays nicely. Chloe lives inside Close and operates like a team member who never takes a day off.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "What does Chloe actually do?",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Calls incoming leads the moment they arrive.",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " No more waiting for a rep to check the queue. Chloe picks up the phone immediately.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ],
        "listItem": "bullet",
        "level": 1
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Qualifies prospects through real conversations.",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " She asks the right questions, identifies intent, and separates hot leads from tire-kickers.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ],
        "listItem": "bullet",
        "level": 1
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Books meetings automatically.",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " Once a lead qualifies, Chloe schedules a meeting and updates the CRM without anyone lifting a finger.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ],
        "listItem": "bullet",
        "level": 1
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Updates contact records in real-time.",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " Every conversation, every qualification detail, every booking—all logged without manual data entry.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ],
        "listItem": "bullet",
        "level": 1
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "The speed-to-lead problem has plagued sales teams for decades. Studies consistently show that responding to a lead within the first five minutes dramatically increases conversion rates. Chloe doesn't need five minutes. She responds in seconds.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [
          {
            "_key": "l2",
            "_type": "link",
            "href": "https://refer.close.com/bf9dumgltl5q"
          }
        ],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Experience Chloe in action with a free Close trial",
            "marks": [
              "l2"
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "This isn't a chatbot pretending to be helpful. Chloe conducts actual phone conversations. She sounds natural. She adapts based on responses. And she hands off qualified, booked leads to your human reps ready to close.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "---",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h2",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Core Features That Make Close a Sales Powerhouse",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Chloe gets the headlines, but the foundation beneath her is what makes Close special. Every feature is designed around the daily reality of inside sales work.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h3",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Built-In Calling",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "No more third-party dialers or phone system integrations. Close includes power dialing, predictive dialing, and click-to-call directly in the platform. Call recordings, transcriptions, and notes all tie back to the contact record automatically. Your reps never have to copy-paste call outcomes again.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h3",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "SMS and Text Messaging",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Texting prospects has become essential, especially for quick follow-ups and appointment reminders. Close lets you send and receive SMS messages right from the CRM. Templates, bulk sends, and automated sequences are all available, so texting scales just like email.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h3",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Email Sequences",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Multi-step email sequences are the backbone of modern outbound. Close makes building them intuitive. Set delays, A/B test subject lines, and track opens and replies. When someone responds, the sequence automatically stops—no awkward double emails.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h3",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Visual Pipeline Management",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Drag-and-drop pipeline views give you instant clarity on where every deal stands. Custom stages, weighted probabilities, and filtering by rep, source, or deal size keep your forecast accurate and your team focused.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h3",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Automated Workflows",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Trigger actions based on events. New lead comes in? Send a welcome email and assign it to a rep. Deal moves to negotiation? Notify the manager. Rep hasn't followed up in three days? Send a reminder. Close's workflow engine handles the busywork so your team sells.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h3",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Reporting and Analytics",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Real-time dashboards show call volume, email performance, pipeline velocity, and individual rep metrics. No exporting to spreadsheets. No waiting for weekly reports. The data lives where the work happens.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [
          {
            "_key": "l3",
            "_type": "link",
            "href": "https://tonyciencia.com/en/posts/how-to-use-close"
          }
        ],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Learn how to use Close for maximum sales impact",
            "marks": [
              "l3"
            ]
          }
        ]
