          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Startups scaling their sales function",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " benefit from Close's simplicity. You don't need a dedicated admin to configure it. New reps get productive within hours, not weeks.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Agencies and consultancies",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " that sell through direct outreach appreciate the unified communication hub. Every touchpoint with a prospect is logged and accessible.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "B2B sales teams",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " running outbound campaigns find Close's sequences and automation invaluable. The combination of email, SMS, and calling in one platform eliminates the tool sprawl that slows most teams down.",
