        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "The full experience. 1,500 AI credits per user, advanced automation, and everything you need to scale. For teams serious about leveraging AI to multiply their output, this tier delivers.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Annual billing saves up to 50%, and every plan includes a free trial—no credit card required. The AI credits refresh monthly, and additional credits are available if you need more capacity.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "What strikes me about Close's pricing is the transparency. No hidden fees. No per-minute charges on calling. No surprise add-ons that double your bill. You know exactly what you're paying for.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
