            "text": "Getting Started: Your First Week with Close",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Setting up Close is refreshingly straightforward. Here's what the onboarding looks like:",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Day 1:",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " Sign up, import your contacts (CSV, direct integrations, or API), and configure your pipeline stages. Most teams have this done in under an hour.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Day 2:",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " Set up your calling preferences, connect your email, and build your first sequence. Close walks you through each step.",
