        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h2",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Why Close Stands Out in a Crowded CRM Market",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "The CRM space is packed with options. Salesforce dominates enterprise. HubSpot owns the inbound marketing angle. Pipedrive targets simplicity.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Close carves its lane by being unapologetically focused on sales execution. It doesn't try to be a marketing platform or a customer service tool. It helps salespeople sell, and it does that exceptionally well.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "The addition of Chloe takes this further. While other CRMs bolt on AI features as afterthoughts, Close built an AI agent that's core to the experience. She's not a gimmick. She's a genuine force multiplier for teams that need to move fast.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "With 2 billion calls, emails, and texts already processed through the platform, Close has the data and infrastructure to back up its promises. The 4.7-star G2 rating reflects real user satisfaction, not manufactured reviews.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [
          {
            "_key": "l6",
            "_type": "link",
            "href": "https://tonyciencia.com/en/posts/why-choose-close"
