            "text": "Chloe is Close's built-in AI sales agent that automatically calls incoming leads, qualifies them through real phone conversations, books meetings, and updates your CRM records—all without human intervention. She's native to the platform, not a third-party integration.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
